data.description: Nestled in the sought after community of Magnolia Reserve you will find this beautiful home located on half an acre. The interlacing of custom paint, stone, brick and covered front porch add character to the residence. Just past the entry take a glimpse of the open concept floor plan and culinary-inspired kitchen overseen by granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and gas cook top with custom backsplash. Primary suite features natural light, trace ceiling and en suite upgraded custom bathroom oasis featuring seamless glass shower, dual sinks and a soaking tub. Transitioning to the backyard this home features large covered patio with outdoor kitchen, custom upgraded ceiling and ceiling fan to keep you cool on warm days! Oversized 3 car epoxied garage with plenty of driveway space for extra parking.
